(25,	1,	'2015-07-14 12:12:12',	'2015-07-14 09:12:12',	'<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span class=\"xr_tc xr_s5\">Dear Sirs and Madams!</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"xr_s4\"><strong><span class=\"xr_tc xr_s4\">We are pleased to invite you to our Camping #1 “KYIV” , located in the parkland of city, in the </span> <span class=\"xr_tc xr_s4\">picturesque landscape of National complex \"Expocenter of Ukraine\" . This place is situated in immediate </span> <span class=\"xr_tc xr_s4\">proximity to Kyiv Circular Road with direction to Odessa, Lviv, Kharkov and Dnipropietrovs’k.</span></strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"xr_s4\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"xr_s4\"><span class=\"xr_tl xr_s1\">Here you will find:</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"xr_s4\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"xr_s4\"><span class=\"xr_tl xr_s2\">- 300 places for motorhomes and caravans on a green grass </span></div>\r\n<div class=\"xr_s4\"><span class=\"xr_tl xr_s2\">- Asphalted camper-ground for 50 places</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"xr_s4\"><span class=\"xr_tl xr_s2\">- Tent camp </span></div>\r\n<div class=\"xr_s4\"><span class=\"xr_tl xr_s2\">- Cars and motorcycles parking </span></div>\r\n<div class=\"xr_s4\"><span class=\"xr_tl xr_s2\">- Electric outlet 220V </span></div>\r\n<div class=\"xr_s4\"><span class=\"xr_tl xr_s2\">- Showers, water supply, toilets facilities </span></div>\r\n<div class=\"xr_s4\"><span class=\"xr_tl xr_s2\">- WiFi Internet</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"xr_s4\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"xr_s4\"><span class=\"xr_tl xr_s2\">Also:</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"xr_s4\"><span class=\"xr_tl xr_s2\">- Small cafe on the Camping site </span></div>\r\n<div class=\"xr_s4\"><span class=\"xr_tl xr_s2\">- Selling souvenirs and accessories for camping </span></div>\r\n<div class=\"xr_s4\"><span class=\"xr_tl xr_s2\">- Assistance in organization of sightseeing and cultural </span> <span class=\"xr_tl xr_s2\">programs </span></div>\r\n<div class=\"xr_s4\"><span class=\"xr_tl xr_s2\">- Bicycle hire